name: The SEO Whiz
description:
My name is Jeff Millett and I’m an experienced SEO consultant. I know what it takes to rank Your Website in today’s highly competitive (highly sensitive) internet playing field.
I have dominated in a number of niche industries over the last 10 years but none of my success brings me more joy than the ones I’m about to tell you about. As a full-time SEO consultant, I’ve had the privilege of working with dozens of businesses owners, in numerous industries, on many different websites.
